%26#039;ve never organized an event before\'/][contact-field label=\'Please give a brief description of the events you%26#039;ve been involved in organizing and what your role was.\' type=\'textarea\'/][contact-field label=\'Do you have at least 2 co-organizers?\' type=\'radio\' options=\'Yes - I have co-organizers already,Nope - but I know some people who might be interested,Nope - I probably need help to find co-organizers,Nope - I want to do it by myself\'/][contact-field label=\'What%26#039;s your relationship to your co-organizers?\' type=\'radio\' options=\'We work for the same company,We%26#039;re friends,We%26#039;ve collaborated on projects before,We met through the meetup group/other tech event\'/][contact-field label=\'Please enter the names and email addresses of your co-organizers here.\' type=\'textarea\'/][contact-field label=\'Are you confident you can raise money from local sponsors to cover the event costs?\' type=\'radio\' options=\'Yes - I%26#039;m cool with the fundraising,I%26#039;m not sure -- I haven%26#039;t done this before but I%26#039;ll do my best,Not really - I hate asking people for money\'/][contact-field label=\'If there are businesses already interested in sponsoring%26#x002c; list them here.\' type=\'textarea\'/][contact-field label=\'Do you know local people who would make good presenters/speakers?\' type=\'radio\' options=\'Yes - I know lots of local WordPress users/developers,Yes - I know a couple of people who would be qualified,No - I don%26#039;t know anyone local who could speak\'/][contact-field label=\'Please enter the names of the people you have in mind%26#x002c; and describe them in a few words.\' type=\'textarea\'/][contact-field label=\'Do you have any connections to potential venue donations (colleges%26#x002c; offices%26#x002c; etc)?\' type=\'radio\' options=\'Yes - I%26#039;ve been talking to people already,No - but I have some leads,No - I%26#039;ll be looking for a venue from scratch\'/][contact-field label=\'Wha